data.description: ***SELLLER IS OFFERING BUYER $5,000 CREDIT WITH FULL PRICE OFFER***  Check out this 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home located in Beecher, Illinois. It's a perfect starter home or if you're looking to downsize, this property is eagerly awaiting your personal touches! You'll love the abundance of kitchen cabinets and countertop space, as well as the large laundry room with a slop sink. Plant lovers will enjoy the big windows throughout the property that let in plenty of natural light. It comes with a convenient attached 1-car garage and an additional attached shed for all your storage needs. The spacious backyard is perfect for outdoor fun! New FELDCO windows with warranty that is transferrable to the new buyers. Newer water heater and Central AC 2021.  Don't miss out on this fantastic home! Call today for your own private showing! **HOME SALE IS CONTINGENT ON SELLER FINDING SUITABLE HOUSING**
